data.description: Wow! This stunning large beautiful home is a gem! As soon as you step inside, you'll be amazed by the large living room with its charming plant shelves and inviting fireplace. With 5 generously sized bedrooms, including both downstairs and upstairs primary suites, as well as a cleverly connected Jack & Jill bathroom for the spare rooms, this home offers an abundance of space and convenience. The kitchen is a true masterpiece, boasting beautiful dark wood cabinets, a convenient wet bar, and exquisite marble countertops, all appliances included!  A raw iron railing leads to a large loft upstairs with a door that opens to a balcony overlooking the pool, while another bedroom also enjoys access to a balcony on the opposite side of the house. The backyard has a large patio and pool perfect for relaxing or entertaining. While the front yard has ample storage space in the three-car garage. And the seller just installed a new water heater! Conveniently located near shopping, and schools.
